snippet.title: Deep Fighter - DreamON Preview Trailer
snippet.description:
Video taken from Dream ON Vol.7
Deep Fighter - Dreamcast
Developer: Criterion Games
Publisher: Ubisoft

Become a Deep Fighter and save the Colony from terrible submarine pirates. A complex tale of intrigue and betrayal will bring you in the abyss on the blue Ocean. Mission after mission, you will discover breathtaking underwater landscapes and its inhabitants.
